ading-module__rvMliW__offsetTop" id="vercel-cli-overview"></span><span class="linked-heading-module__rvMliW__title [&amp;&gt;p]:m-0">Vercel CLI Overview</span></h1></div><div class="p-0 m-0 flex flex-wrap gap-2 items-center justify-between list-none w-full pt-2 pb-4 mb-4 border-b border-gray-400" data-exclude-from-llms="true"><div class="lg:hidden flex items-center gap-2.5"><button class="bg-transparent border-none p-0 m-0 font-inherit cursor-pointer text-sm text-gray-900 flex items-center gap-1 transition-all hover:text-gray-1000 " type="button"><svg data-testid="geist-icon" height="16" stroke-linejoin="round" style="width:12px;height:12px;color:currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M2.8914 10.4028L2.98327 10.6318C3.22909 11.2445 3.5 12.1045 3.5 13C3.5 13.3588 3.4564 13.7131 3.38773 14.0495C3.69637 13.9446 4.01409 13.8159 4.32918 13.6584C4.87888 13.3835 5.33961 13.0611 5.70994 12.7521L6.22471 12.3226L6.88809 12.4196C7.24851 12.4724 7.61994 12.5 8 12.5C11.7843 12.5 14.5 9.85569 14.5 7C14.5 4.14431 11.7843 1.5 8 1.5C4.21574 1.5 1.5 4.14431 1.5 7C1.5 8.18175 1.94229 9.29322 2.73103 10.2153L2.8914 10.4028ZM2.8135 15.7653C1.76096 16 1 16 1 16C1 16 1.43322 15.3097 1.72937 14.4367C1.88317 13.9834 2 13.4808 2 13C2 12.3826 1.80733 11.7292 1.59114 11.1903C0.591845 10.0221 0 8.57152 0 7C0 3.13401 3.58172 0 8 0C12.4183 0 16 3.13401 16 7C16 10.866 12.4183 14 8 14C7.54721 14 7.10321 13.9671 6.67094 13.9038C6.22579 14.2753 5.66881 14.6656 5 15C4.23366 15.3832 3.46733 15.6195 2.8135 15.7653Z" fill="currentColor"/></svg>Ask AI about this page</button></div><div class="text-sm text-gray-900 whitespace-nowrap">Last updated<!-- --> <!-- -->March 11, 2026</div></div><div class="[&amp;_[data-geist-note]_p]:my-0 hover:[&amp;_[data-geist-note]_a]:no-underline! [&amp;_code_p]:my-0 [&amp;_code_p]:contents [&amp;_ol]:p-0 [&amp;_ol]:pl-4 [&amp;_p]:leading-[160%] [&amp;_ol]:list-decimal [&amp;_ol]:ml-0 md:[&amp;_ol]:ml-1 [&amp;_[class*=&#x27;container&#x27;]_p]:m-0"><p class="my-4">Vercel gives you multiple ways to interact with and configure your Vercel Projects. With the command-line interface (CLI) you can interact with the Vercel platform using a terminal, or through an automated system, enabling you to <a data-zone="same" class="link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__blend" href="/docs/cli/logs">retrieve logs</a>, manage <a data-zone="same" class="link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__blend" href="/docs/cli/certs">certificates</a>, replicate your deployment environment <a data-zone="same" class="link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__blend" href="/docs/cli/dev">locally</a>, manage Domain Name System (DNS) <a data-zone="same" class="link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__blend" href="/docs/cli/dns">records</a>, and more.</p>
<p class="my-4">If you&#x27;d like to interface with the platform programmatically, check out the <a data-zone="same" class="link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__blend" href="/docs/rest-api">REST API documentation</a>.</p>
<div class="linked-heading-module__rvMliW__container"><h2 class="linked-heading-module__rvMliW__header text-heading-20 sm:text-heading-32" data-components-heading="true"><span class="linked-heading-module__rvMliW__target" id="installing-vercel-cli"></span><a class="linked-heading-module__rvMliW__title [&amp;&gt;p]:m-0" href="#installing-vercel-cli">Installing Vercel CLI</a><a href="#installing-vercel-cli" class="linked-heading-module__rvMliW__permalink" aria-label="Copy link to section"><svg class="text-[0.6em]" data-testid="geist-icon" height="16" stroke-linejoin="round" style="color:currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z" fill="currentColor"/></svg></a></h2></div>
<p class="my-4">To download and install Vercel CLI, run the following command:</p>
<!--$?--><template id="B:1"></template><div class="group/copy my-4 relative rounded-md border border--gray-400 overflow-hidden" aria-label="Code block - Terminal"><div class="@container py-2 pr-3 pl-4 rounded-t-md border-b border-gray-400 min-h-12 bg-background-200"><div class="flex items-center gap-x-10 gap-y-3 flex-wrap @[400px]:flex-nowrap"><div class="text-gray-900 flex items-center gap-2 m-0 text-[13px] min-w-0 mr-auto pl-3 @[400px]:pl-0"><div class="size-4"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" height="16" width="16" data-slot="geist-icon" style="color:currentColor"><path fill="currentColor" fill-rule="evenodd" d="m1.53 12.78-.53.53-1.06-1.06.53-.53L4.19 8 .47 4.28l-.53-.53L1 2.69l.53.53L5.6 7.29a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.42zm7.22-.28H8V14h8v-1.5H8.75" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></div>Terminal</div><div class="flex gap-1 items-center shrink-0"><span class="block rounded-full after:rounded-full after:animate-loading-skeleton relative overflow-hidden after:content-[&quot;&quot;] after:absolute after:inset-0 after:right-[-200%] after:bg-gradient-to-r after:from-[var(--ds-gray-100)] after:via-[var(--ds-gray-200)] after:to-[var(--ds-gray-100)] after:bg-[length:50%_100%] after:bg-[position:0_0]" data-geist-skeleton="" data-testid="legacy/skeleton" data-version="v1" style="width:72px;min-height:32px"></span></div></div></div><div class="relative rounded-md border border-[var(--ds-gray-400)] overflow-hidden group/copy [&amp;_.line]:before:!hidden border-none my-0" data-geist-code-block=""><button type="button" tabindex="0" data-react-aria-pressable="true" aria-label="Copy to clipboard" data-testid="copy/button" class="outline-none m-0 border-0 align-baseline no-underline group/trigger relative cursor-pointer select-none transform translate-z-0 flex text-[var(--themed-fg,_var(--ds-background-100))] bg-[var(--themed-bg,_var(--ds-gray-1000))] font-medium !px-(--geist-gap-half) max-w-full items-center justify-center transition-[border-color, background,color,transform,box-shadow] duration-[