<div class="linked-heading-module__rvMliW__container"><h2 class="linked-heading-module__rvMliW__header text-heading-20 sm:text-heading-32" data-components-heading="true"><span class="linked-heading-module__rvMliW__target" id="updating-vercel-cli"></span><a class="linked-heading-module__rvMliW__title [&amp;&gt;p]:m-0" href="#updating-vercel-cli">Updating Vercel CLI</a><a href="#updating-vercel-cli" class="linked-heading-module__rvMliW__permalink" aria-label="Copy link to section"><svg class="text-[0.6em]" data-testid="geist-icon" height="16" stroke-linejoin="round" style="color:currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z" fill="currentColor"/></svg></a></h2></div>
<p class="my-4">When there is a new release of Vercel CLI, running any command will show you a message letting you know that an update is available.</p>
<p class="my-4">If you have installed our command-line interface through <a href="http://npmjs.org/" rel="noopener" target="_blank" data-zone="null" class="link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__blend">npm</a> or <a href="https://yarnpkg.com" rel="noopener" target="_blank" data-zone="null" class="link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__blend">Yarn</a>, the easiest way to update it is by running the installation command yet again.</p>
